This skill (`zerion-sendai-ideas`) is adapted from SendAI / Superteam's
`solana-new` idea skills:

  https://github.com/sendaifun/solana-new/tree/main/skills/idea

The interview frameworks, scoring rubrics, validation sprints, landscape
mappings, and DefiLlama playbooks in `SKILL.md` are derived from that work,
condensed into a single umbrella skill, and adapted by Zerion to compose
with the `zerion` CLI.

The upstream MIT license is reproduced below. Modifications by Zerion.

